{"id": "1497604898781663323", "channel_id": "1497587575962206309", "type": 0, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "1. yes you should use R wheels. They are better than most of the wheels on your team. Higher rarity does not mean better. I would also take off Path Forsaken from jenkin and put Analysis of Death\n\n2. you should be pulling for a wide variety of units so you have more teambuilding options. caecus and nautila are not very good in this team\n\n3. if you want to make your life easier, pull for arachne or another limited carry. E3 lotan is not much better than jenkin\n\n4. R wheels are not \"buffed for story mode\" they were always good and you never realized", "timestamp": "2026-04-25T14:27:12.023000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1497587575962206309", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "unsure on how to progress the story levels", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747333490184292"]}
